snippet.title: [Indie MMORPG] [Unity 3D] Reign of Darkness Update 9
snippet.description:
Help the Darkness Grow!!!  : )
https://www.patreon.com/posts/33001531

Just polishing a few things before setting it live on early access. This video I was trying to show the new features like disenchant, enchant, using Transmute in the Philosopher's Pouch,  the bank tabs(which will be much smaller on release), multi-spec'ing(hybrid classes), spending skills points and refunding them, and dungeon difficulty settings(Reg, Med, Hard). Almost there! :)

Background Music and Ambience by this awesome guy here
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCscIWGhDNOHmLu3OLgpU5vA
